AI-Document Standardizer 

An automated technical writing tool designed to eliminate structural documentation drift, reduce friction in engineering team
offboardings/onboardings, and implement a rigid "Documentation-as-Code" standard. This web application transforms chaotic, 
unformatted engineer logs and rough notes into production-grade, compliance-ready Markdown documents (SOPs, Runbooks, and Knowledge Bases) 
using deterministic AI layout replication.
